  <md:title>Diseases Associated with Depressed or Overactive Immune Responses </md:title>
  <md:abstract><para id="para-00001">By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list id="list-00001">
<item>Discuss inherited and acquired immunodeficiencies</item>
<item>Explain the four types of hypersensitivity and how they differ</item>
<item>Give an example of how autoimmune disease breaks tolerance</item>
</list></md:abstract>
